<P>Mrs. Berkeley.&mdash;<Q REND="inline">"Yes, very well.</Q></P>
<P>Mr. B.&mdash;<Q REND="inline">"Do you remember his &s;aying jocularly to you,
that he believed that it was written by me?</Q></P>
<P>Mrs. B.&mdash;<Q REND="inline">"Yes.</Q></P>
<P>Mr. B.&mdash;<Q REND="inline">"And do you remember what an&s;wer you made?</Q></P>
<P><PB N="clxxxiv" REF="196">Mrs. B.&mdash;<Q REND="inline">"Yes, that I would freely give a thou&s;and
pounds that you were capable of writing that letter.</Q></P>
<P>Mr. B.&mdash;<Q REND="inline">"Well, my dear Madam, perhaps it may now
give you &s;ome little plea&s;ure to hear that your <HI>Bairn</HI> did
