him&s;elf bringeth his MOTHER to &s;hame<NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">Proverbs xix. chap. 20.</NOTE>;"</Q> which &s;eems
to imply, that in tho&s;e <HI>ignorant, unenlightened</HI> times the
<PB N="cxcv" REF="207">
