<P>Dr. B.&mdash;<Q REND="inline">"Eliza LAWRENCE! what do you mean, child?
are you going to &s;leep after your <HI>long</HI> journey?"</Q></P>
<P><PB N="dcxxi" REF="635">Mr. B.&mdash;<Q REND="inline">"No, my dear Sir, no; but I can't help &s;up|po&s;ing,
that there mu&s;t be &s;ome <HI>&s;pell</HI> in the thirteen
