<L>Lamented ROBERT! thou, who&s;e &s;potle&s;s brea&s;t</L>
<L>No &s;in polluted, no remor&s;e oppre&s;s'd!</L>
<L>Ble&s;s'd with the art affection to engage<NOTE N="&dagger;" PLACE="foot">He
had been always told that God &s;aw <HI>all</HI> that pa&s;&s;ed in his heart;
