<L>Stranger alike to ev'ry vice and fear!</L>
<L><PB N="171" REF="813"> Oft, as returning, this lov'd &s;chool I &s;ee,</L>
<L>Once ble&s;s'd with joy, and liveline&s;s, and thee,</L>
<L>Still from my bo&s;om &s;teal unbidden &s;ighs,</L>
